ISLAMABAD, Mar 22 (APP):Prime Minister Imran Khan will address the nation at 3:30 PM, said Special Assistant to Prime Minister on Information and Broadcasting Dr Firdous Ashiq Awan.
In a tweet she said, the prime minister in this important address will express his views on challenges posed by coronavirus in the country.
